title: Oltári csajok
resume: Three sisters in their twenties, pursuing success and love in the big city. The story opens with an engagement party that runs astray, leaving the future wedding gift of a real-life fairytale palace up for grabs. Thus, a race begins between the sisters to be the first to find and marry their own Prince Charming.
